WEBVTT

00:16.306 --> 00:19.230
-ARE WE THERE, YET?
-ALMOST.

00:19.230 --> 00:21.852
WAIT, WE'RE NOT DOING THAT
BLINDFOLDED SURFING
THING AGAIN, ARE WE?

00:21.852 --> 00:25.146
'CAUSE THAT DIDN'T
EXACTLY END UP BEING
ONE OF YOUR BETTER IDEAS.

00:25.146 --> 00:27.818
