WE'RE NOT GOING SURFING.

00:30.451 --> 00:33.324
AT LEAST NOT YET.

00:33.324 --> 00:36.787
OKAY.
DO YOU RECOGNIZE IT?

00:36.787 --> 00:39.500
-NO.
-NO?

00:39.500 --> 00:43.464
UNLESS IT'S THE GRASSY CLEARING
IN DOLPHIN'S COVE,
RIGHT BY THE LIFEGUARD TOWER,

00:43.464 --> 00:45.756
WHICH HAPPENS TO BE
THE EXACT SPOT WE MET

00:45.756 --> 00:49.340
THREE MONTHS AGO TO THIS DAY.

00:49.340 --> 00:52.343
TO THE MINUTE, ACTUALLY.

00:52.343 --> 00:55.136
(laughs) AT THE BEGINNING
OF WHAT'S TURNED OUT TO BE

00:55.136 --> 00:58.599
THE MOST BODACIOUS
SUMMER OF MY LIFE.

00:58.599 --> 01:01.772
EVEN THE PART
WHEN WE GOT TRAPPED
IN A 1960S BEACH MOVIE.

01:01.772 --> 01:03.484
(laughs)

01:06.317 --> 01:08.239
BRADY, IT'S BEAUTIFUL.

01:08.239 --> 01:11.612
I HAD TO DO SOMETHING COOL
FOR OUR MEET-IVERSARY.

01:11.612 --> 01:14.535
IT ALL HAPPENED RIGHT HERE.
YOU WERE WALKING ON THE BEACH.

01:14.535 --> 01:16.907
I SAT THERE WATCHING
WET SIDE STORY
ON MY TABLET.

01:16.907 --> 01:20.501
AND I THOUGHT,
"WHO IS THE SURFER DUDE
WITH THE SHINY HAIR?"

01:20.501 --> 01:22.463
AND YOU SAID,

01:22.463 --> 01:25.085
"WANNA WATCH
THE AWESOMEST MOVIE
EVER MADE?"

01:25.085 --> 01:28.169
AND I SAID, "I DON'T THINK
'AWESOMEST' IS A REAL WORD.

01:28.169 --> 01:30.381
AND EVEN IF IT WAS,
THAT MOVIE'S DEFINITELY NOT IT."

01:30.381 --> 01:33.714
THEN I SAID,
"CHECK IT OUT WITH ME.

01:33.714 --> 01:36.517
"IF YOU DON'T HAVE A GOOD TIME,
I'LL BUY YOU A MANGO SMOOTHIE.

01:36.517 --> 01:40.100
EITHER WAY, YOU WIN."
AND...

01:40.100 --> 01:44.395
-AND I DO LOVE MANGOES.
-YEAH.

01:44.395 --> 01:47.528
YOU DID ALL THIS FOR ME?

01:47.528 --> 01:50.491
I'D SWIM
TO CHINA FOR YOU.

01:50.491 --> 01:53.073
OR HAWAII.

01:53.073 --> 01:54.825
OR WHATEVER'S THAT WAY.

01:54.825 --> 01:56.697
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT'S THAT WAY.

01:56.697 --> 01:58.539
(laughs)

01:58.539 --> 02:01.372
-YOU READY?
-MM-HM.

02:03.374 --> 02:05.416
(exhales)

02:05.416 --> 02:09.169
Tanner: IN A WAY, IT'S ALMOST
TOO BAD IT'S ALMOST ALL OVER.

02:09.169 --> 02:13.844
