-MACK, HEY.
-HEY.

44:25.834 --> 44:29.748
-WHO'S-- WHO'S THIS?
-THIS IS, UH, MY COUSIN,

44:29.748 --> 44:33.211
DELGA, FROM FINLAND.

44:36.885 --> 44:38.717
YOU ARE SO CUTE.

44:38.717 --> 44:41.009
(chuckles)
HEY, LISTEN, UH,

44:41.009 --> 44:44.012
I HOPE I DIDN'T CAUSE ANY
PROBLEMS BETWEEN YOU
AND BRADY YESTERDAY.

44:44.012 --> 44:47.145
OH, NO, NO.
OUR PROBLEMS ARE...
ARE TOTALLY OUR OWN.

44:47.145 --> 44:48.897
FAIR ENOUGH.

44:48.897 --> 44:51.359
HEY, HOW'S THE, UH,
SAVE THE BEACH DANCE
SHAPING UP?

44:51.359 --> 44:54.442
IT'S OKAY.
UH, WE HAVEN'T REALLY
SOLD MANY TICKETS,

44:54.442 --> 44:56.404
SO JUST HOPING PEOPLE
WILL SHOW UP.

44:56.404 --> 44:58.616
OH, I'M SURE THEY WILL.
IT'S-- IT'S A GREAT CAUSE.

44:58.616 --> 45:04.622
-(laughs)
