A REALLY BIG GLOVE.

45:11.039 --> 45:12.791
OH, SO YOU CAN CATCH US.

45:12.791 --> 45:14.672
(chuckles)

45:14.672 --> 45:15.834
OKAY.

45:17.095 --> 45:19.097
THERE'S GOING
TO BE A DANCE?

45:19.097 --> 45:20.428
THIS WORLD JUST GETS
BETTER AND BETTER.

45:20.428 --> 45:22.390
YEAH, UNTIL YOUR
FORMERLY ADORABLE BOYFRIEND

45:22.390 --> 45:24.302
STARTS ACTING LIKE
A COMPLETELY DIFFERENT PERSON.

45:24.302 --> 45:26.935
TRUST ME, LELA,
YOU'RE BETTER OFF
IN YOUR WORLD,

45:26.935 --> 45:29.227
WHERE BOYS ARE
SIMPLE AND RELIABLE.

45:29.227 --> 45:32.440
-MACK!
-OH, HI.

45:32.440 --> 45:34.022
UH, HI.

45:34.022 --> 45:36.694
-THIS IS, UMM...
-LELA.

45:36.694 --> 45:39.237
I'M HERE TO DISCOVER
WHO I AM AND FIND FULFILLMENT.

45:41.529 --> 45:43.701
A WOMAN THAT KNOWS
WHAT SHE WANTS.
I LIKE HER.

45:43.701 --> 45:46.785
