-I DID MY PHILOSOPHY CAMP THESIS
ON FEMALE SELF-EMPOWERMENT.

45:46.785 --> 45:49.327
I CAN REBUILD
A MOTORCYCLE.

45:49.327 --> 45:51.870
REALLY? I'M LOOKING
INTO BUYING A SCOOTER.

45:51.870 --> 45:55.213
I'D LOVE YOUR PERSPECTIVE
ON ENGINE TORQUE DIFFERENTIALS.

45:55.213 --> 45:57.585
OH, I CAN GO ON AND ON
ABOUT TORQUE!

45:57.585 --> 46:00.048
