46:00.048 --> 46:03.681
(scoffs) IT'S A DISASTER.
SHE LOVES EVERYTHING.

46:03.681 --> 46:04.973
EVEN MR. TERRY'S
CHEMISTRY CLASS.

46:04.973 --> 46:07.385
SHE TITRATED
HER SODIUM HYDROXIDE PERFECTLY

46:07.385 --> 46:10.228
AND LOVED THE WAY
THE RESULTING SOLUTION
MATCHED HER SHOES.

46:10.228 --> 46:13.151
WELL, I THINK
I'M WEARING DOWN
TANNER A LITTLE.

46:14.192 --> 46:16.484
NUGGETS MADE
OUT OF CHICKEN?

46:16.484 --> 46:18.987
AMAZING! (laughs)

46:20.158 --> 46:21.279
-OR NOT.
-(whimpers)

46:21.279 --> 46:23.161
DON'T WORRY,
I HAVE A PLAN.

46:23.161 --> 46:24.782
WE TURN THEM LOOSE, ALONE,

46:24.782 --> 46:28.746
IN THE MOST DANGEROUS,
CONFUSING, SCARY
PLACE IMAGINABLE.

46:28.746 --> 46:33.081
A PLACE WHERE
ONE FALSE MOVE RESULTS
IN EXILE, SHAME, HORROR...

46:33.081 --> 46:35.753
WAIT, WH-- WHERE?

46:37.045 --> 46:38.256
Brady:
THE CAFETERIA.

46:39.547 --> 46:40.919
(both laugh)

46:42.380 --> 46:44.973
-(screech)
-(laughing)

46:48.386 --> 46:49.637
OKAY.

46:51.269 --> 46:55.353
-HI, WE'RE NEW HERE.
-I COULD CARE LESS, SPRAY-TAN.

46:55.353 --> 46:57.565
(laughing)

46:57.565 --> 47:00.278
ACTUALLY, IT'S TANNER.
(laughs)

47:00.278 --> 47:02.490
NO SPRAY,
ADD AN "ER". TANNER.

47:02.490 --> 47:05.403
-(laughs)
TANNER LEWIS READY DANGER.
-(grunts)

47:05.403 --> 47:06.824
-OH, NO, I--
-(grunts)

47:06.824 --> 47:07.906
-WHA-- I--
-(grunts)

47:07.906 --> 47:08.947
-I MEA--
-(grunts)

47:08.947 --> 47:10.578
-I W-- TH-- B--
-(grunts)

47:10.578 --> 47:14.332
GET OUT OF MY FACE.
(laughing)

47:15.333 --> 47:16.454
(grunts)

47:18.126 --> 47:21.880
-(grunts)
-TANNER, ARE YOU
GETTING THE IMPRESSION

47:21.880 --> 47:25.263
