A LITTLE STAND-OFFISH

47:25.263 --> 47:27.385
AND, WELL, MEANISH?

47:27.385 --> 47:31.309
RIGHT?
AND ANGRYISH, TOO.

47:31.309 --> 47:35.353
LIKE THE BIKERS AND SURFERS,
ONLY ANGRYISHER.

47:38.106 --> 47:41.109
