ANYONE CAN DO IT.

47:48.616 --> 47:51.289
-IT'S ATTACHED TO YOU,
HERE ON YOUR FACE.
-(yelps)

47:51.289 --> 47:54.412
-(laughs)
-THERE ARE 43 MUSCLES TO USE.

47:54.412 --> 47:57.795
♪ JUST GOTTA PUT 'EM
IN THE RIGHT PLACE ♪

47:57.795 --> 48:00.498
♪ IF WE CAN DO IT,
