51:49.647 --> 51:51.819
OH, LELA. HI.
UM... (clears throat)

51:51.819 --> 51:54.822
WANNA HANG OUT?
I'VE BEEN WORKING
ON SOME NEW LOOKS.

51:54.822 --> 51:58.866
CHECK 'EM OUT.
I CALL THIS ONE
THOUGHTFUL HANDSOME.

51:58.866 --> 52:01.869
THIS ONE'S SOULFUL SMOLDER.

52:01.869 --> 52:04.372
(laughs)
THOSE ARE WONDERFUL,
TANNER, BUT I CAN'T.

52:04.372 --> 52:07.505
WE HAVE CALCULUS HOMEWORK.
IT'S SO EXCITING.

52:07.505 --> 52:12.089
OH. OH, OKAY.
UH, WELL, HAVE FUN...
(chuckles)

52:15.173 --> 52:16.424
WITHOUT ME.

52:20.888 --> 52:23.221
WE'RE FURTHER THAN EVER
FROM TALKING THEM
INTO GOING BACK.

52:23.221 --> 52:25.022
YOU WATCH LELA,
I'LL WATCH TANNER.

52:25.022 --> 52:26.103
(sighs)

52:27.185 --> 52:29.227
